<div id="review_2440569729" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2440569729" />
    <a title="Wayne Barrett" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/21372390-wayne-barrett"><img alt="Wayne Barrett" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1625178759p2/21372390.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2440569729?book_show_action=true">Oct 25, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Wayne Barrett" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Wayne Barrett" href="/user/show/21372390-wayne-barrett">Wayne Barrett</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Audible Audio " href="/book/show/24890653-the-wolf-s-hour">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/21372390-wayne-barrett?shelf=horror">horror</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/21372390-wayne-barrett?shelf=holocaust">holocaust</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/21372390-wayne-barrett?shelf=2018">2018</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/21372390-wayne-barrett?shelf=thriller">thriller</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/21372390-wayne-barrett?shelf=war">war</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/21372390-wayne-barrett?shelf=historical">historical</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/21372390-wayne-barrett?shelf=werewolves">werewolves</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2440569729" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2519086907885580392">Werewolves, sex, spies, assassins, nazis... man this book had it all. <br/><br/>This was not so much a scary book as it was an action packed thriller. McCammon does provide some gruesome scenes along the way, so scary or not, this is still a horror novel fit for a good pre-Halloween read. <br/><br/>Along the way we are given some back-story glimpses of our protagonists life and his transformation into a lycanthrope, but the bulk of the story deals with him in human form as an undercover agent endeavoring to aid the</span>
  <span id="freeText2519086907885580392" style="display:none">Werewolves, sex, spies, assassins, nazis... man this book had it all. <br /><br />This was not so much a scary book as it was an action packed thriller. McCammon does provide some gruesome scenes along the way, so scary or not, this is still a horror novel fit for a good pre-Halloween read. <br /><br />Along the way we are given some back-story glimpses of our protagonists life and his transformation into a lycanthrope, but the bulk of the story deals with him in human form as an undercover agent endeavoring to aid the allies in the battle against Hitler and his Nazi regime. <br /><br />I thought this was an entertaining, exciting read, from the first page to the very end. I wouldn't call it perfect, but deserving of 5 stars.</span>
  <a data-text-id="2519086907885580392" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

